{"tid":2439949,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場詳細訪問左七個親建制媒體工作嘅前記者 佢地全部都話報道會有政治審查","createTime":"2021-03-09T15:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T16:03:23.000Z","uid":22556,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"872efc82946fa59681cfd687cf1b61db57334088","tid":2439949,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:03:22.000Z","msg":"《立場》訪問七名在親建制媒體工作的記者，一致指出，政治審查在反送中期間浮現。<br />\n<br />\n不願透露工作機構的前港聞記者 Julice（化名）觀察，政治審查由以往較敏感的「保安 beat」，急速擴散至日常新聞。由 2019 年七一佔領立法會起，她察覺管理層態度轉變，八月後報章標題屢遭修改，避免提及示威者受傷數字、催淚彈數字 &mdash; 除了一兩次嚴重事件之外，僅能在內文提及。「起咗題，出咗街，第二日會改咗，」她質疑有意對警方行為作出淡化，「條題係負面針對警方，就唔會放大個位。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/media/%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E-1-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%BC%95%E7%87%83%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%89%E6%93%87-%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7/?fbclid=IwAR1cG2srqKrH1ClT_u8dv-U_MKAutyhLHWU8_jK8Ao6FRAfGzvnsOreWCTY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2F%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B0%258E-1-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BC%2595%25E7%2587%2583%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%258A%2589%25E6%2593%2587-%25E5%25A0%2585%25E6%258C%2581%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%259B%25A2%25E8%2581%25B7%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1cG2srqKrH1ClT_u8dv-U_MKAutyhLHWU8_jK8Ao6FRAfGzvnsOreWCTY&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy5LdSN32AczdJcE5lfwVwJ8%3D&h=d944a1de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2F%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B0%258E-1-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BC%2595%25E7%2587%2583%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%258A%2589%25E6%2593%2587-%25E5%25A0%2585%25E6%258C%2581%25E9%2582%2584